<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <title>OTP Verification | {{companyName}}</title>
  <style>
    /* CSS RESET */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100% !important;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7f9fc 0%, #edf1f7 100%);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Arial', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }
    table {
      border-collapse: collapse !important;
      width: 100%;
    }
    img {
      border: 0;
      height: auto;
      line-height: 100%;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE CONTAINER */
    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* CARD DESIGN */
    .email-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(13, 42, 87, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e8edf5;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d2a57 0%, #1a3f8c 100%);
      padding: 28px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .company-logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .header-title {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* BODY CONTENT */
    .email-body {
      padding: 40px 35px;
    }
    .greeting {
      color: #0d2a57;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .message {
      color: #4a5568;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    /* OTP CONTAINER */
    .otp-container {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9f6 0%, #fff4ef 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #ffe8dc;
    }
    .otp-label {
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      display: block;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e85b0f;
      letter-spacing: 10px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding: 0 10px;
      display: inline-block;
      position: relative;
    }
    .otp-code::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -8px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 200px;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e85b0f, transparent);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .otp-expiry {
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .expiry-timer {
      color: #e85b0f;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* CTA BUTTON */
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e85b0f 0%, #f07c3a 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(232, 91, 15, 0.2);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4530d 0%, #e86f2f 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(232, 91, 15, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* SECURITY NOTE */
    .security-note {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-left: 4px solid #0d2a57;
      padding: 18px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .security-title {
      color: #0d2a57;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .security-text {
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .email-footer {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e8edf5;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .social-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 8px;
      padding: 8px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .social-icon:hover {
      background: #e8edf5;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .contact-info {
      color: #4a5568;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .contact-link {
      color: #e85b0f;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .copyright {
      color: #a0aec0;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    /* MOBILE RESPONSIVE */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .header-title {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 36px;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
      }
      .cta-button {
        padding: 14px 30px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 400px) {
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 32px;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 25px 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <table class="email-card" role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <!-- HEADER -->
      <tr>
        <td class="email-header">
          <div class="header-badge">
            <span class="company-logo">{{companyName}}</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="header-title">Verify Your Account</h1>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- BODY -->
      <tr>
        <td class="email-body">
          <h2 class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</h2>
          
          <p class="message">
            You've requested to verify your account. Use the One-Time Password (OTP) below to complete your sign-in process.
          </p>

          <!-- OTP CONTAINER -->
          <div class="otp-container">
            <span class="otp-label">Your verification code</span>
            <div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>
            <div class="otp-expiry">
              Expires in: <span class="expiry-timer">10 minutes</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- CTA BUTTON -->
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="cta-button">Verify Account Now</a>
          </div>

          <p class="message">
            For security reasons, please do not share this OTP with anyone. Our team will never ask for your verification code.
          </p>

          <!-- SECURITY NOTE -->
          <div class="security-note">
            <div class="security-title">
              <span>üîí Security Notice</span>
            </div>
            <p class="security-text">
              This OTP was generated on {{generatedTime}}. If you didn't request this verification, please ignore this email or 
              <a href="{{supportLink}}" style="color: #e85b0f; font-weight: 500;">contact our support team</a> immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="message" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            Having trouble with the OTP? You can also verify your account by clicking the button above.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <tr>
        <td class="email-footer">
          <p class="footer-text">
            Need help? We're here for you. Visit our 
            <a href="{{helpCenterLink}}" style="color: #e85b0f; font-weight: 500;">Help Center</a> 
            or reply to this email for assistance.
          </p>

          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="#" class="social-icon">üåê Website</a>
            <a href="#" class="social-icon">üì± Mobile App</a>
            <a href="#" class="social-icon">üíº LinkedIn</a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-info">
            <p>
              {{companyName}}<br />
              {{companyAddress}}<br />
              Email: <a href="mailto:{{companyEmail}}" class="contact-link">{{companyEmail}}</a><br />
              Phone: <a href="tel:{{companyPhone}}" class="contact-link">{{companyPhone}}</a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="copyright">
            ¬© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.<br />
            This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>